videos.description: J'Von McCormick pulls up and connects on a 3, then Jared Harper hits back-to-back long balls to tie the Gators at 19-19.
videos.headline: Auburn ties game with 3 straight triples

videos.description: Samir Doughty dumps it down low for Chuma Okeke, who slams it down with Kevarrius Hayes all over his back.
videos.headline: Auburn's Okeke powers up for big finish

videos.description: Andrew Nembhard lobs it to the rim from out of bounds, and Kevarrius Hayes finishes the alley-oop with a thunderous two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Hayes flushes alley-oop on Florida's inbound play

videos.description: Jared Harper swings a pass to Bryce Brown, who nails a 3-pointer over Kevarrius Hayes to give Auburn some breathing room against Florida.
videos.headline: Brown sinks rainbow 3 to extend Tigers' lead

videos.description: Jared Harper pulls up in front of Jalen Hudson and knocks down a huge 3-pointer, putting the Tigers ahead 64-60 with just 12 seconds left.
videos.headline: Harper nails clutch 3 for Auburn

videos.description: Andrew Nembhard appears to get fouled on his game-tying 3, but the referees don't call it, and Auburn escapes with a 65-62 win over Florida.
